&lt;h2 dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;margin-top:18pt;margin-bottom:4pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:17pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;What are the small actions that help protect the seas of Cat Ba and Lan Ha Bay?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;The waters of Cat Ba and Lan Ha Bay are home to an extremely sensitive ecosystem of coral reefs and seagrass. To follow the &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Green Travel Guide: Protecting Cat Ba&#039;s Forests and Seas with Small Actions&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt; on the water, pay attention to the following details:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Limit the use of chemical sunscreens: Chemicals such as oxybenzone can cause coral bleaching. Prioritize ocean-friendly physical (mineral) sunscreens.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Kayak instead of taking motorboats: This not only lets you enjoy the bay&#039;s tranquility but also reduces noise and emissions harmful to marine life.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Do not dump waste directly into the sea: When on a cruise boat, make sure waste is processed according to proper procedures; do not throw toilet paper or leftover food into the bay.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Join beach clean-ups on wild beaches: A small action like picking up a few pieces of ghost nets or plastic bottles washed ashore is also a way for you to practice the &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Green Travel Guide: Protecting Cat Ba&#039;s Forests and Seas with Small Actions&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
