&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Choosing local services is also an important part of responsible tourism. To systematize the &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Green Travel Guide: Protecting Cat Ba&#039;s Forests and Seas with Small Actions&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;, you should:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Prioritize homestays or green hotels: Places that have energy- and water-saving systems and limit single-use items.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Enjoy local specialties: Consuming food on the spot helps reduce the carbon emissions from transportation and supports the local economy.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Say no to wildlife products: Absolutely do not buy souvenirs made from coral, rare seashells, or medicines and foods derived from wild animals.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
