&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:13pt;color:#e74c3c;background-color:#ffffff;vertical-align:baseline;&quot;&gt;In addition, discover many more high-quality travel experiences at&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://vietnamtoure.com/&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:13pt;color:#e74c3c;background-color:#ffffff;vertical-align:baseline;&quot;&gt; Vietnamtoure.com&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
